.DT
set_pick_skill
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_pick_skill

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_pick_skill -  This sets the skill that will be used when attempting to pick the lock.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_pick_skill(string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - The skill to use when picking the lock.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/close_lock.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This sets the skill that will be used when attempting to
pick the lock.  By default it is set to "covert.lockpick.safes"
so it need only be changed if you want to check a different
skill.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_pick_skill(), set_difficulty()
.EP

